headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Test Track: Try Out the Emperor Vectre, Pfister Astron, and the Dewbauchee Vagner
content: Looking for a new set of wheels? Visit the LS Car Meet’s Test Track to see if the Emperor Vectre, Pfister Astron or Dewbauchee Vagner fit the bill. Pit them against each other in a Scramble, race the clock in a Time Trial, or throw smoke — all at no cost to you.
